text: Daisy Siete () is a Philippine television drama anthology broadcast by GMA Network. Starring the SexBomb Girls, it premiered on September 1, 2003 on the network's afternoon line up. The show concluded on July 2, 2010 with a total of 26 seasons. It was replaced by Ang Yaman ni Lola in its timeslot. ==Seasons== Seasons 2 to 5 were weekly episodes, where the story is not continuous. {| class="wikitable" ! Season !
